message.entry: The input image must be a grayscale or RGB image, or a batch of images.
The input embeddings must be a 64-by-64-by-256 single array.
The input point prompts must be a P-by-2 numeric array.
The input bounding box prompt must be a 1-by-4 numeric vector.
The input mask logits box prompt must be a 256-by-256-by-1 single array. This is the output of a previous run of segmentObjectsFromEmbeddings method.
Insufficient or invalid prompts. Please specify at least one, or both of valid ForegroundPoints and BoundingBox prompts.
The image size must be a 1-by-2, or a 1x3 vector.
The segmentAnythingModel object requires Computer Vision Toolbox license.
